CONTEXT LeftResidualTypeMismatchCheck IN ENGLISH

PURPOSE CONTEXT LeftResidualTypeMismatchCheck
{+ Test that left residual fails when targets cannot be joined.
   This verifies the type checker correctly rejects r[A*B]/s[B*C] due to mismatched targets. +}

RELATION r[A*B]
RELATION s[B*C]
RELATION result[A*B]

RULE testLeftResidualFail: result = r/s

ENDCONTEXT
